     20            ******************************************************************************
     21            @verbatim
     22            ==============================================================================
     23                         ##### I2C peripheral extension features  #####
     24            ==============================================================================
     25          
     26            [..] Comparing to other previous devices, the I2C interface for STM32F427xx/437xx/
     27                 429xx/439xx devices contains the following additional features :
     28          
     29                 (+) Possibility to disable or enable Analog Noise Filter
     30                 (+) Use of a configured Digital Noise Filter
     31          
     32                               ##### How to use this driver #####
     33            ==============================================================================
     34            [..] This driver provides functions to configure Noise Filter
     35              (#) Configure I2C Analog noise filter using the function HAL_I2C_AnalogFilter_Config()
     36              (#) Configure I2C Digital noise filter using the function HAL_I2C_DigitalFilter_Config()
     37          
     38            @endverbatim
     39            */
